title: Stimulus, Carlyle Group's David Rubenstein

Guests: Josh Wingrove, Bloomberg White House reporter, Sarah Ponczek, Bloomberg markets reporter, Former Florida Congressman Patrick Murphy, Lester Munson, Principal at government relations firm, BGR Group, and David Rubenstein, Carlyle Group Co-Founder and author of "How to Lead."
